Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.54,0:24:48.42,Default,,0,0,50,,If you're a man, let's put your strength to test{男だったら　力を試せ}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.42,0:24:52.37,Default,,0,0,50,,If you are a man, keep your hopes sizzling{男だったら　希望(のぞみ)を燃やせ}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.37,0:24:56.59,Default,,0,0,50,,If you are a man, don't lose your heart{男だったら　くじけるな}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.59,0:25:04.96,Default,,0,0,50,,Because there's just you and me, a man and a man{俺もおまえも　男と男}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.42,0:25:13.34,Default,,0,0,50,,With crimson blood flowing in our veins all the same{おなじ真赤な　血が通う}
